  "time_ut": 1662384334,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b95\u0b9a\u0bc0\u0ba9\u0bc8 \u0b92\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc8\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The person who came to hand over the magazine was arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police said that a person who came to Pananturai North Police to hand over a magazine containing 30 bullets used for Ri 56 rifle, claiming to have found it at the Galli Mukatital protest site, has been arrested.",
        "The police said that a 35-year-old man from Panandura Gorakana area who came to the police station with a magazine containing bullets has been arrested.",
        "He has testified that the magazine was believed to belong to the gun of a security guard who was on duty at the Khali Mukhatal protest site and was found lying there.",
        "However, the police said that investigations are on as to how the suspect got hold of the magazine containing the bullets and whether he was involved in any criminal activity."
      ],
